 39→ * Feature: 041-falcon-instance-lookup
 40→ * Task: T027
 41→ *
 42→ * Format: i-[0-9a-fA-F]{8,17}
 43→ */
 44→const AWS_INSTANCE_ID_REGEX = /^i-[0-9a-fA-F]{8,17}$/i;
